                          Iggy Azalea - Change Your Life (EP)


2013 EP from the Hip Hop sensation. Australian born, now residing in Atlanta, Iggy Azalea has spent the last year building an incredible buzz. Discovered by T.I., Iggy has gained the respect of Hip-Hop heavyweights. The cult classic mixtape Ignorant Art catapulted her into the spotlight in 2011. The Glory EP featured Mike Posner, BOB & Pusha T. Iggy's first official Island release, "Work" proved to everyone that she's a real artist with a flow to be reckoned with . The Change Your Life EP serves as an appetizer to her full-length debut The New Classic.
